text.tspan: All types of the qubes are built on top of a template, which can
be based on any type of operating system.
When handling untrusted files or browsing the internet
anonymously, use disposable qubes that erased when done.
Isolate all of your device drivers and services which directly
connect to the internet in their own dedicated qubes
Are where end user applications are run. They can be configured
on a per app or multiple app basis as per isolation needs
